<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
  <title>FAQ</title>
  <style>
    /* General Reset and Base Styles */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background-color: #121212; /* Dark background */
      color: #f5f5f5; /* Light text for readability */
      line-height: 1.6;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    /* Header Styles */
    header {
      background-color: #1f1f1f; /* Slightly lighter dark for contrast */
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #ff4500; /* Orange highlight */
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5em;
      color: #ff4500; /* Orange accent */
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    header p {
      font-size: 1.1em;
      color: #ddd;
    }

    /* Main Content Styles */
    main {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #1c1c1c; /* Slightly lighter background for content area */
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    section {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #444; /* Subtle divider between sections */
      padding-bottom: 15px;
    }

    section h2 {
      font-size: 1.8em;
      color: #ff4500; /* Orange accent for headings */
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    section p {
      font-size: 1.1em;
      color: #ddd; /* Light text */
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    section ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
      list-style-type: disc;
    }

    section ul li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    /* Footer Styles */
    footer {
      background-color: #1f1f1f;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px;
      border-top: 2px solid #ff4500;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    footer p {
      color: #ddd;
      font-size: 0.9em;
    }

    /* Links */
    a {
      color: #ff4500;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      header h1 {
        font-size: 2em;
      }

      main {
        padding: 15px;
      }

      section h2 {
        font-size: 1.5em;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
  <p>Your common questions answered</p>
</header>

<main>
  <section>
    <h2>1. What is the purpose of this website?</h2>
    <p>This website is designed to connect food donors with those in need. We aim to reduce food waste and help communities.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>2. How can I donate food?</h2>
    <p>To donate food, create an account, log in, and click the "Donate Food" button. Fill in the required details, and your donation will be listed for others to find.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>3. Is there a fee for using this service?</h2>
    <p>No, this service is completely free to use for both donors and recipients.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>4. How do I find donations near me?</h2>
    <p>Use the "Find Donations" feature to search for food donations near your location by entering your city or address.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>5. Can I edit or remove my donation?</h2>
    <p>Yes, you can edit or remove your donation by visiting your account dashboard and managing your listings.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>6. Who can I contact for further support?</h2>
    <p>If you need further assistance, please <a href="/contactus">contact us</a> using the Contact Us page.</p>
  </section>
</main>

<footer>
  <p>&copy; 2025 foDonor All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
